### Data Classification Model

In this project, I stepped into the world of Machine Learning. The goal was to build a classification model that can automatically categorize data.
Using the Scikit-learn and Pandas libraries, I trained a model to identify patterns in a dataset and make accurate predictions.

## Key Skills:

-Data preprocessing with Pandas.
-Splitting datasets into training and testing sets.
-Training machine learning models and evaluating their accuracy.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- NumPy
